==English==

===Verb===
'''to [[cast]] [[off]]'''

#{{transitive}} to [[discard]] or [[reject]] something
#{{transitive}},{{nautical}} to [[let go]] a [[cable]] or [[rope]] securing a [[vessel]] to a [[buoy]], [[wharf]] etc so that she may [[proceed]]
#{{intransitive}} to finish the last [[row]] of [[knitted]] [[stitch]]es and remove them securely from the [[needle]]

